\c 26
\s Izigaba zabalindi bamasango lezabaphathi bemisebenzi
\p
\v 1 Ngezigaba zabalindi bamasango. KwabakoKora kwakunguMeshelemiya indodana kaKore wamadodana kaAsafi.
\v 2 LoMeshelemiya wayelamadodana\x + 9.21.\x*, uZekhariya izibulo, uJediyayeli owesibili, uZebhadiya owesithathu, uJathiniyeli owesine,
\v 3 uElamu owesihlanu, uJehohanani owesithupha, uEliyohenayi owesikhombisa\x + 9.21.\x*.
\v 4 UObedi-Edoma laye wayelamadodana, uShemaya izibulo, uJehozabadi owesibili, uJowa owesithathu, uSakari owesine, loNethaneli owesihlanu\x + 15.18,24. 16.38.\x*,
\v 5 uAmiyeli owesithupha, uIsakari owesikhombisa, uPhewulethayi owesificaminwembili; ngoba uNkulunkulu wayembusisile.
\v 6 LakuShemaya indodana yakhe kwazalwa amadodana abusa jikelele endlini kayise, ngoba ayengamaqhawe alamandla\x + 26.4.\x*.
\v 7 Amadodana kaShemaya: O-Othini, loRefayeli, loObedi, uElizabadi, abafowabo, amadodana alamandla, oElihu loSemakhiya\x + 26.9. 2 Kho. 2.16.\x*.
\v 8 Bonke laba babengabamadodana kaObedi-Edoma, bona lamadodana abo labafowabo, amadoda enelisayo ngamandla omsebenzi, bengamatshumi ayisithupha lambili bakoObedi-Edoma.
\v 9 Njalo uMeshelemiya\x + 26.1.\x* wayelamadodana labafowabo, amadodana alamandla, elitshumi lesificaminwembili\x + 26.9. 2 Kho. 2.16.\x*.
\v 10 UHosha laye emadodaneni kaMerari wayelamadodana, uShimiri inhloko (lanxa wayengeyisilo izibulo, kodwa uyise wamenza waba yinhloko\x + 26.16. 16.38.\x*);
\v 11 uHilikhiya owesibili, uTebaliya owesithathu, uZekhariya owesine; wonke amadodana labafowabo bakaHosa babelitshumi lantathu.
\v 12 Phakathi kwalabo kwakulezigaba zabalindi bamasango; izinhloko zamadoda zilemilandu njengabafowabo, ukukhonza endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 13 Basebesenza inkatho yokuphosa, omncinyane laye njengomkhulu, ngokwendlu yaboyise, besenzela isango lesango\x + 24.31.\x*.
\v 14 Inkatho yempumalanga yawela-ke phezu kukaShelemiya; basebesenza inkatho yokuphosa ngoZekhariya indodana yakhe, umeluleki ohlakaniphileyo; inkatho yakhe yasiphuma ngenyakatho\x + 24.31.\x*.
\v 15 KuObedi-Edoma ngeningizimu; lakumadodana akhe, indlu yokulondoloza.
\v 16 KuShupimi lakuHosa ngentshonalanga, lesango iShalekethi\x + Isa. 6.13.\x* elisemgwaqweni\x + 26.18. 2 Kho. 12.20.\x* omkhulu oya phezulu, umlindi ngomlindi\x + 1 Kho. 10.5. 2 Lan. 9.4. Neh. 3.31.\x*.
\v 17 Ngempumalanga kwakulamaLevi ayisithupha, ngenyakatho abane ngosuku, ngeningizimu abane ngosuku, leziphaleni ababili \add ng\add*ababili;
\v 18 eParibari ngentshonalanga\x + 2 Kho. 23.11.\x*, abane emgwaqweni omkhulu, ababili eParibari\x + 26.18. 2 Kho. 12.20.\x*.
\v 19 Lezi yizigaba zabalindi bamasango bamadodana amaKora\x + 26.1.\x* labamadodana kaMerari\x + 26.10.\x*.
\p
\v 20 LakumaLevi, uAhiya wayephethe izinto eziligugu zendlu kaNkulunkulu, njalo wayephethe izinto eziligugu zezinto ezingcwele\x + 28.12. 26.22,24,26. 29.8. Ezra 2.69. Neh. 10.38. 12.44. 13.12. Mal. 3.10.\x*.
\v 21 Amadodana kaLadani, abantwana bomGerishoni uLadani, kaLadani umGerishoni, inhloko zaboyise zazingoJehiyeli.
\v 22 Amadodana kaJehiyeli: UZethamu, loJoweli umfowabo, babephethe izinto eziligugu zendlu yeN\nd kosi\x + 23.8.\x*\nd*.
\v 23 KumaAmramu, kumaIzihari, kumaHebroni, kumaUziyeli\x + 23.12.\x*.
\v 24 LoShebuweli indodana kaGereshoma indodana kaMozisi wayeyisiphathamandla phezu kwezinto eziligugu\x + 23.16,17.\x*.
\v 25 Labafowabo abakaEliyezeri: ORehabhiya indodana yakhe\x + 23.16,17.\x*, loJeshaya indodana yakhe, loJoramu indodana yakhe, loZikiri indodana yakhe, loShelomithi indodana yakhe\x + 24.21.\x*.
\v 26 UShelomithi lo labafowabo babephethe zonke izinto eziligugu zezinto ezingcwele uDavida inkosi ayezingcwelisile, lenhloko zaboyise, lenduna zezinkulungwane lezamakhulu, labalawulimabutho\x + 2 Sam. 8.11.\x*.
\v 27 Kokwempi lokwempangweni bakungcwelisela ukulungisa indlu yeN\nd kosi\x + 2 Sam. 8.11.\x*\nd*.
\v 28 Lakho konke uSamuweli umboni ayekungcwelisile\x + 29.29. 1 Sam. 9.9.\x*, loSawuli indodana kaKishi loAbhineri indodana kaNeri\x + 2 Sam. 2.8.\x* loJowabi indodana kaZeruya\x + 2 Sam. 2.32.\x*; konke okwakungcwelisiwe kwakungaphansi kwesandla sikaShelomithi labafowabo.
\p
\v 29 KumaIzihari uKenaniya lamadodana akhe babengabomsebenzi wangaphandle phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + Neh. 11.16.\x*, beyizinduna bengabahluleli\x + 23.4. Dute. 16.18.\x*.
\v 30 KumaHebroni uHashabhiya labafowabo, amadoda alamandla, ayinkulungwane lamakhulu ayisikhombisa, babephethe iziphathamandla zakoIsrayeli nganeno kweJordani ngentshonalanga, emsebenzini wonke kaJehova lenkonzweni yenkosi\x + 27.17.\x*.
\v 31 KumaHebroni uJeriya wayeyinhloko\x + 23.19.24.23.\x*, kumaHebroni, ngokwezizukulwana zaboyise. Ngomnyaka wamatshumi amane wokubusa kukaDavida adingwa, kwasekutholwa phakathi kwawo amaqhawe alamandla eJazere yeGileyadi\x + 6.81. Nani 21.32. Josh. 21.39.\x*.
\v 32 Labafowabo amadoda alamandla ayezinkulungwane ezimbili lamakhulu ayisikhombisa, inhloko zezindlu. UDavida inkosi wasebenza abaphathi phezu kwabakoRubeni labakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase ezintweni zonke zikaNkulunkulu lezinto zenkosi\x + 2 Lan. 19.11.\x*.
